title: Jeremy Corbyn refuses to comment on new reports of 'close links' to IRA
text: Jeremy Corbyn has refused to comment on new reports of his and shadow Chancellor John McDonnell 's alleged "close links" to the IRA . Archived documents showed Mr Corbyn attended several events supporting the IRA in the 1980s and '90s, and
